<h2>Judo</h2>
<p><strong>Basic description</strong> - private, partner and semi-private judo lessons for adults</p>
<p><strong>Benefits</strong> - In addition to the technical and self-defense benefits, kosen judo offers anaerobic, aerobic, full body strength and flexibility training.  Increases your confidence on your feet as well as on the ground.</p>
