<h2>No-gi Judo</h2>
<p><strong>Basic description</strong> - private, partner and semi-private no-gi judo lessons for adults</p>
<p><strong>Benefits</strong> - In addition to the technical and self-defense benefits, no-gi judo offers anaerobic, aerobic, full body strength and flexibility training.  Increases your confidence on your feet and compliments your jiu-jitsu or MMA training.</p>
