<h2>Kosen Judo</h2>
<p><strong>Basic description</strong> - private, partner and semi-private judo lessons for adults</p>
<p><strong>Benefits</strong> - In addition to the technical and self-defense benefits, no-gi judo offers anaerobic, aerobic, full body strength and flexibility training.  Increases your confidence on the ground in a low-impact fashion.</p>  
<p><strong>Details</strong> - Style of judo where extra focus is given on the groundwork techniques including pins, chokes, and armlocks.  Basic elements and fundamentals such as grips, posture, proper base and fluid body movements are emphasized.  You will sweat and be challenged physically and mentally.</p>

<h2>Self-defense for women</h2>
<p><strong>Basic description</strong> - private, partner and semi-private self-defense for women</p>
<p><strong>Benefits</strong> - Increase your awareness and confidence while learning how to protect yourself.  Even the odds of surviving a life-threatening situation.</p>
<p><strong>Details</strong> - Tips, tactics and techniques both standing and on the ground are taught to help you avoid being a victim.  Repetitive drilling and realistic training methods are used to mimic a real-life situation.  Classes are taught by 2x Olympian and 5th degree black belt Valerie Gotay.  Excellent for teenage girls as well.</p>

