<p><strong>Benefits</strong> - increased lean muscle, strength and power, improved mobility, agility, coordination, aerobic and anaerobic threshold, and fat loss.</p>
<p><strong>Details</strong> - Get in shape and improve your physical fitness with our own system of training using a mixture of grappling drills/exercises and full body functional exercises.  Free weights, medicine balls, ropes, cones, boxes, agility ladder, etc. may be used.  Exercise programs are tailored to your level of fitness, but you will be challenged.</p>